令\(g(x) = f(x) - t = x^{3} - 3x^{2} + 3 - t\)，
则\(g(x) = 0\)的三个根分别为\(x_{1} < x_{2} < x_{3}\)，\par
则\(g(x) = (x - x_{1})(x - x_{2})(x - x_{3}) = x^{3} - (x_{1} + x_{2} + x_{3})x^{2} + (x_{1}x_{2} + x_{2}x_{3} + x_{1}x_{3})x - x_{1}x_{2}x_{3}\)\par
所以\(\left\{ \begin{array}{r}
x_{1} + x_{2} + x_{3} = 3 \\
x_{1}x_{2} + x_{2}x_{3} + x_{1}x_{3} = 0 \\
x_{1}x_{2}x_{3} = t - 3
\end{array} \right.\)，\par
由于\(- 1 < t < 3\)，所以\(- 4 < x_{1}x_{2}x_{3} = t - 3 < 0\)，即\(x_{1}x_{2}x_{3}\)的取值范围是\(( - 4,0)\)，故B不正确；\par
由\(\left\{ \begin{array}{r}
x_{1} + x_{2} + x_{3} = 3 \\
x_{1}x_{2} + x_{2}x_{3} + x_{1}x_{3} = 0 \\
x_{1}x_{2}x_{3} = t - 3
\end{array} \right.\)，可得：\(x_{1} + x_{3} = 3 - x_{2}\)，\(x_{1}x_{3} = - x_{2}\left( x_{1} + x_{3} \right) = - x_{2}\left( 3 - x_{2} \right)\)，\par
则\(x_{1}x_{3} = - x_{2}\left( 3 - x_{2} \right)\)，因为\(0 < x_{2} < 2\)，所以当\(x_{2} = \frac{3}{2}\)时，\(\left( x_{1}x_{3} \right)_{\min} = - \frac{3}{2}\left( 3 - \frac{3}{2} \right) = - \frac{9}{4}\)，\par
由于\(x_{1}x_{3} < 0\)，所以\(x_{1}x_{3}\)的取值范围是\(\left\lbrack - \frac{9}{4},0 \right)\)，故C正确；\par
对于D，\(\left( x_{3} - x_{1} \right)^{2} = {(x_{1} + x_{3})}^{2} - 4x_{1}x_{3} = {(3 - x_{2})}^{2} + 4x_{2}(3 - x_{2})\)，\par
所以\(\left( x_{3} - x_{1} \right)^{2} = {(3 - x_{2})}^{2} + 4x_{2}(3 - x_{2}) = - 3{(x_{2} - 1)}^{2} + 12\)，\par
因为\(0 < x_{2} < 2\)，所以当\(x_{2} = 1\)时，\(\left( x_{3} - x_{1} \right)^{2}{}_{\max} = 12\)，且\(\left( x_{3} - x_{1} \right)^{2} > - 3{(0 - 1)}^{2} + 12 = 9\)；\par
所以\(\left( x_{3} - x_{1} \right)^{2}\)的取值范围是\((9,12\rbrack\)，故D正确}
\end{question}

