\begin{question}
若"\(\forall\alpha \in \left( 0,\frac{\pi}{2} \right),\frac{1}{\sin^{2}\alpha} + \frac{4}{\cos^{2}\alpha} \geq m^{2} + 1\)恒成立"为真命题，
则实数\(m\)的取值范围是
.
\topics{根据全称命题的真假求参数；基本不等式求和的最小值；函数不等式恒成立问题}
\difficulty{0.65}
\answer{\(\left\lbrack - 2\sqrt{2},2\sqrt{2} \right\rbrack\)}
\explain{因为\(\forall\alpha \in \left( 0,\frac{\pi}{2} \right),\frac{1}{\sin^{2}\alpha} + \frac{4}{\cos^{2}\alpha} \geq m^{2} + 1\)，
令\(f(\alpha) = \frac{1}{\sin^{2}\alpha} + \frac{4}{\cos^{2}\alpha},\alpha \in \left( 0,\frac{\pi}{2} \right)\)，\par
则\(m^{2} + 1 \leq \left\lbrack f(\alpha) \right\rbrack_{\min}\)，\par
\(f(\alpha) = \frac{1}{\sin^{2}\alpha} + \frac{4}{\cos^{2}\alpha} = \frac{\sin^{2}\alpha + \cos^{2}\alpha}{\sin^{2}\alpha} + \frac{4\left( \sin^{2}\alpha + \cos^{2}\alpha \right)}{\cos^{2}\alpha} = 1 + 4 + \frac{\cos^{2}\alpha}{\sin^{2}\alpha} + \frac{4\sin^{2}\alpha}{\cos^{2}\alpha}\geq 5 + 2\sqrt{4} = 9\)，\par
当且仅当\(\frac{\cos^{2}\alpha}{\sin^{2}\alpha} = \frac{4\sin^{2}\alpha}{\cos^{2}\alpha}\)，
即\(\tan\alpha = \frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\)时取等号，\par
所以\(m^{2} + 1 \leq 9\)，
解得\(- 2\sqrt{2} \leq m \leq 2\sqrt{2}\)，\par
即实数\(m\)的取值范围是\(\left\lbrack - 2\sqrt{2},2\sqrt{2} \right\rbrack\).\(\left\lbrack - 2\sqrt{2},2\sqrt{2} \right\rbrack\).}
\end{question}

\begin{question}
在\(\triangle ABC\)中，
内角\(A,B,C\)所对的边分别为\(a,b,c\)，
该三角形面积大小记为\(S\)，
则\(\frac{16S}{a^{2} + b^{2} + 2c^{2}}\)的最大值为
.
\topics{三角形面积公式及其应用；余弦定理解三角形；基本不等式求积的最大值}
\difficulty{0.4}
\answer{\(\frac{4\sqrt{5}}{5}\)/\(\frac{4}{5}\sqrt{5}\)}
\explain{由三角形面积\(S = \frac{1}{2}ab\sin C\)，
余弦定理\(c^{2} = a^{2} + b^{2} - 2ab\cos C\)，\par
有\(a^{2} + b^{2} = c^{2} + 2ab\cos C\)，\par
则\(\frac{16S}{a^{2} + b^{2} + 2c^{2}} = \frac{16 \times \frac{1}{2}ab\sin C}{a^{2} + b^{2} + 2\left( a^{2} + b^{2} - 2ab\cos C \right)} = \frac{8ab\sin C}{3a^{2} + 3b^{2} - 4ab\cos C}\)\par
由基本不等式\(a^{2} + b^{2} \geq 2ab\)当且仅当\(a = b\)时取等号，
则\(3a^{2} + 3b^{2} \geq 6ab\)，\par
所以\(\frac{8ab\sin C}{3a^{2} + 3b^{2} - 4ab\cos C} \leq \frac{8ab\sin C}{6ab - 4ab\cos C} = \frac{\text{4sin}C}{3 - 2\cos C}\)，\par
令\(t = \frac{\text{4sin}C}{3 - 2\cos C}\)，
则\(\text{4sin}C + 2t\cos C = 3t\)，\par
根据辅角公式\(\text{4sin}C + 2t\cos C = \sqrt{16 + 4t^{2}}\sin(C + \varphi)\)，\par
其中\(\cos\varphi\text{=}\frac{4}{\sqrt{16 + 4t^{2}}}\text{,sin}\varphi = \frac{2t}{\sqrt{16 + 4t^{2}}}\)，
即\(\sqrt{16 + 4t^{2}}\sin(C + \varphi) = 3t\)，\par
因为\(\sin(C + \varphi) \in \lbrack - 1,1\rbrack\)，
所以\(\sqrt{16 + 4t^{2}} \geq |3t|\)，
两边平方可得\(16 + 4t^{2} \geq 9t^{2} \Rightarrow t^{2} \leq \frac{16}{5}\)，\par
则\(\frac{16S}{a^{2} + b^{2} + 2c^{2}}\)的最大值为\(\frac{4\sqrt{5}}{5}\).\(\frac{4\sqrt{5}}{5}\).}
\end{question}

